Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.70,0:38:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(326,465)}Ne, to je v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.26,0:38:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,464)}Tebe to také zraňuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.04,0:39:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,462)}Můžeme zkusit jiné metody...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.89,0:39:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(313,462)}To je moje povinnost.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.24,0:39:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(317,463)}Promiň.
