Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.99,0:39:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(305,460)}Ne, to platí i pro tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.79,0:39:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(317,460)}Ahoj.
